{
  "stem": "3150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when you-- when you went to work, it was really a blessing at that time because somehow you always managed to steal something, you know, to-- to bring home.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because if you would sit in the ghetto, I mean, there was only bricks and-- and dirt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That-- that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But at least when you went to work, so you either stole apples or pears, or-- to bring-- to bring something home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at this point, what they did, they brought another town by the name of Truvets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, god.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "T-R-U-V-E-T-Z, I think, is the closest I can come to it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this shtetl was a little bigger than ours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would take a guess, probably about 1,000 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they fenced off half of the town and they put us all on this--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at my house, if I can remember correctly, there must have been probably between 30 and 40 people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, because we had to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took half of the town and brought in another town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was really-- I mean, we used our barn, which we had for people to live.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a real-- a real ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you couldn't-- it was fenced off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What was the fence made out of?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you remember what it looked like?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Plain-- plain, you know, wire with the-- sticky wire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't the electric wire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not electrified.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in and out, you have to have a passport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have to have the not a passport, but a [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] permission, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So some things were permitted to-- to come in and out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also, at the same time, they-- they they gave us the yellow-- the yellow Magen David to wear.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
